    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，那数字平台开发者的角色定位是什么？是实际的人还是泛指团队？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "developer",
        "Digital platform Developer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "是实际的人，Person类型。另外数字平台本身是一个系统，它会消费数字资产。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "developer",
        "digital_platform",
        "Consumes digital assets"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我把开发者和数字平台都放进企业边界里了。接下来内容分发这块怎么划分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b0",
        "developer",
        "digital_platform"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "内容分发是The Brick Company内部的一个子域，需要再包一层边界。里面有两个核心服务：Briefing Service和OrderList Service。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "b1",
